7HA -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; fix annotations
AY0 -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; fix annotations
FA5 -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; fix annotations
GOM -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; fix annotations
NKS -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; fix annotations
THX -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; fix annotations

0E7 -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; class as non-polymer instead. 
0ZX -- Leaving group annotations which leaves a disconnected type; class as non-polymer instead.

ZPT -- Missing coordinate; Sole usage is for platinum ion, correct accordingly
